text: Mattu avaru helidaru; ‘‘nanna putrare, nivella onde bagilinda pravesisabedi. Pratyeka bagilugalinda pravesisiri. Yavude visayadalli nim'mannu allahaninda raksisalu matra nanage sadhyavilla. Adhikaravellavu allahanige seride. Nanu avanalle bharavase ittiddene mattu bharavase iduvavarellaru avanalle bharavase idabeku’’
